<title>USA: Barrett adopts shareholder rights plan.</title>
<headline>Barrett adopts shareholder rights plan.</headline>
<dateline>DENVER 1997-08-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>Barrett Resources Corp said on Tuesday that it adopted a shareholder rights plan with a 15 percent trigger.</p>
<p>Barrett said in a news release that it adopted the plan to assure fair treatment for its shareholders and to discourage such abusive takeover tactics as partial tender offers.</p>
<p>Barrett mentioned no specific takeover attempt to which it might be reacting.</p>
<p>Barrett is an oil and natural gas exploration and production company.</p>
